SELECT SUM(amount) as amount
FROM recurrings
WHERE space_id = 1 AND YEAR(starts_on) <= '2019' AND MONTH(starts_on) <= '6' AND ((YEAR(ends_on) >= '2019' AND MONTH(ends_on) >= '6') OR ends_on IS NULL)

select sum(`amount`) as aggregate from `spendings` where `spendings`.`space_id` = 1 and `spendings`.`space_id` is not null and YEAR(happened_on) = '2019' AND MONTH(happened_on) = '6' and `spendings`.`deleted_at` is null

select sum(`amount`) as aggregate from `earnings` where `earnings`.`space_id` = 1 and `earnings`.`space_id` is not null and YEAR(happened_on) = '2019' AND MONTH(happened_on) = '6' and `earnings`.`deleted_at` is null

select SUM(amount) total, description from `earnings` where `earnings`.`space_id` = 1 and `earnings`.`space_id` is not null and YEAR(happened_on) = '2019' AND MONTH(happened_on) = '6' and `earnings`.`deleted_at` is null group by `description` order by `total` asc

select SUM(tag_id) total, tag_id, name from `spendings` inner join `tags` on `spendings`.`tag_id` = `tags`.`id` where `spendings`.`space_id` = 1 and `spendings`.`space_id` is not null and YEAR(happened_on) = '2019' AND MONTH(happened_on) = '6' and `spendings`.`deleted_at` is null group by `tag_id` order by `total` asc

SELECT
tags.name AS name,
tags.color AS color,
SUM(spendings.amount) AS amount
FROM
tags
LEFT OUTER JOIN
spendings ON tags.id = spendings.tag_id AND spendings.deleted_at IS NULL
WHERE
tags.space_id = 1 AND YEAR(happened_on) = 2019 AND MONTH(happened_on) = 6
GROUP BY
tags.id
ORDER BY
SUM(spendings.amount) DESC
LIMIT 5;
